# Minimal exclude list for the BigWigsMods packager. Intentionally
# does NOT use `package-as:` (we let the packager use the default
# folder name behaviour, which was working in v0.6.0-beta) and does
# NOT use `manual-changelog:` (auto-generation from commit messages
# was also working previously). Only purpose: keep non-addon files
# (shell scripts, Lua test specs, markdown docs, lint config, type
# stubs) out of the published zip so Wago's fingerprinter sees a
# clean WoW-addon-shaped archive.
#
# CHANGELOG.md and README.md intentionally NOT in the ignore list —
# Wago/CurseForge display them on the project listing.
ignore:
  - scripts
  - spec
  - docs
  - .github
  - .luacheckrc
  - types.lua
